  <brief_title>Treatment Protocol to Monitor the Safety of a 200 mg Dose of Bicalutamide in Patients With Advanced Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Treatment Protocol to Monitor the Safety of a 200 mg Daily Dose of Bicalutamide (Casodex) in Patients With Advanced Prostate Cancer</official_title>
