  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open label, single-centered treatment protocol designed to monitor the safety of
      patients treated with a 200 mg daily dose of CASODEX. Patient will receive CASODEX as long as
      physician feels that he is benefiting from this form of therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
